cc:Work.dc:title: Track map of Mugello
cc:Work.dc:description: Created in Inkscape with data from Google Earth. The gray dashed line represents pavement that has the same width as the main track, but only leads to pit road. Because of its location, the author of this image believes that it is only used by cars needing a shorter route back to the paddock.
